{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/civil-service-government-communication-service/about","content_id":"5f5b9353-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef","description":"We support all professional communicators across government to gain the skills and knowledge they need to carry out their roles.","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><h2 id=\"who-we-are\">Who we are</h2>\n\n<p>The Government Communication Service is a <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/civil-service/about/recruitment#professions\">Civil Service profession</a>. If you are working in communications, or need communications advice or support as part of your role, please get in touch.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"career-opportunities-and-professional-development\">Career opportunities and professional development</h2>\n\n<p>The <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://gcs.civilservice.gov.uk/\">Government Communication Service website</a> is the place where you can engage with your professional community and find out about the learning, qualifications and opportunities available to help you develop your skills.</p>\n\n<p>GCS offers a wide range of different learning opportunities, from traditional classroom-based learning and mentoring to case studies, guides and blog posts from cutting edge government communicators.</p>\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"Updated link to new GCS website.","public_timestamp":"2015-09-29T15:38:49Z"},{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2014-05-01T11:40:41Z"}],"corporate_information_groups":[],"headers":[{"id":"who-we-are","level":2,"text":"Who we are"},{"id":"career-opportunities-and-professional-development","level":2,"text":"Career opportunities and professional development"}],"organisation":"39d7f79d-7470-46bf-8a27-425a9693b984","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"about","first_published_at":"2014-05-01T13:40:41+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/civi